Trovit is a vertical search engine for classifieds (real estate, jobs, cars and products). On March 2012, it became the leading search engine for classified ads in Europe and Latin America. On 2016, Trovit reached 51 countries worldwide, being available in 19 languages and receiving more than 90 million unique visitors every month.
The name "Trovit" is derived from trovitâ€², the Esperanto root for "found".
